      <title>拉马福萨称污水正在毁坏南非人类的摇篮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/cradle-of-humankind-ramaphosa-says-its-being-damaged-by-sewage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨敦促官员阻止污水排放，以免破坏拥有最多古人类化石的旅游景点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/cradle-of-humankind-ramaphosa-says-its-being-damaged-by-sewage</guid>
